<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
  <title>About - National Historic Sites</title>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: page }) %>

  <div class="hero min-h-screen bg-base-200">
    <div class="hero-content text-center">
      <div class="max-w-md">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">About</h1>
        <p class="py-6">This application was created for WEB322 Assignment 5. It showcases National Historic Sites across Canada and allows users to view, add, edit, and delete sites from the collection.</p>
        <p class="py-2">The application uses:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-left">
          <li>Express.js for the server</li>
          <li>EJS for templating</li>
          <li>Sequelize for database operations</li>
          <li>PostgreSQL for data storage</li>
          <li>Tailwind CSS and DaisyUI for styling</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
